      "title": "Combine the equations",
      "content": "Both equations equal $y$, so $$-\\tfrac{1}{7}x=\\tfrac{1}{5}x.$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Solve for $x$",
      "content": "Subtract to get $(-\\tfrac{1}{7}-\\tfrac{1}{5})x=0$. Since the coefficient is nonzero, $x=0$."
    },
